
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>All-Barum (올바름) - 안산 스마트 분리배출 가이드</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Chart.js for beautiful analytics -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <!-- FontAwesome for Premium Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Leaflet Map CSS & JS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css" />
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
    
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        brand: {
                            50: '#f0fdf4',
                            100: '#dcfce7',
                            500: '#10b981',
                            600: '#059669',
                            700: '#047857',
                            900: '#064e3b',
                        }
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Pretendard', 'Inter', 'sans-serif'],
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css');
        body {
            font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, sans-serif;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #f1f1f1;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #10b981;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        #map {
            height: 450px;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        /* Scanner line animation */
        @keyframes scan {
            0%, 100% { top: 0%; }
            50% { top: 100%; }
        }
        .scan-line {
            animation: scan 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <!-- TOP NAVIGATION BAR -->
    <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 cursor-pointer" onclick="switchTab('camera-scanner')">
                <div class="bg-brand-500 text-white p-2.5 rounded-xl shadow-md shadow-brand-500/20">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-recycle text-xl"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <span class="text-xl font-black text-brand-700 tracking-tight">All-Barum</span>
                    <span class="text-xs block text-slate-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">올바름 • Ansan AI Clean Guide</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Language Selector -->
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                <div class="relative inline-block text-left">
                    <select id="langSelect" onchange="changeLanguage(this.value)" class="bg-slate-100 border-0 text-slate-700 text-sm rounded-lg focus:ring-brand-500 focus:border-brand-500 block p-2 font-medium cursor-pointer">
                        <option value="ko">🇰🇷 한국어</option>
                        <option value="en">🇺🇸 English</option>
                        <option value="zh">🇨🇳 中文</option>
                        <option value="vi">🇻🇳 Tiếng Việt</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- BANNER: Welcome and quick translation status -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-600 to-emerald-700 text-white py-3 px-4 text-center text-sm font-medium">
        <span id="bannerText">🌍 안산시 외국인 주민과 내국인 모두를 위한 다국어 AI 스마트 쓰레기 배출 솔루션</span>
    </div>

    <!-- MAIN BODY -->
    <main class="flex-grow max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
        
        <!-- DASHBOARD HERO SECTION (ANALYTICS & INTRO) -->
        <section class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
            <!-- Left Side: Interactive Overview -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-1 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <span class="bg-brand-50 text-brand-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold" id="heroBadge">안산시 AI 환경 비서</span>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-3 leading-snug" id="heroTitle">쓰레기 사진만 찍으세요, 올바름이 다 알려드립니다.</h1>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed" id="heroDesc">
                        국내 최대 외국인 거주지인 안산시의 문화적 다양성을 존중하며, 스마트 카메라 스캔을 통해 언어 장벽 없이 누구나 즉각적이고 올바르게 쓰레기를 처리하도록 돕습니다.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-3.5 rounded-xl">
                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 block" id="stat1Label">안산시 외국인 인구 (25년)</span>
                        <span class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800">54,776명</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-3.5 rounded-xl">
                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 block" id="stat2Label">무단투기 평균 (월간)</span>
                        <span class="text-lg font-bold text-red-500">약 150톤</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Side: Real Data Charts (Demographics and Garbage Trends) -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <!-- Chart 1: Foreign Resident Ratio Trend (2022-2025) -->
                <div>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800" id="chart1Title">안산시 연도별 인구 구조 변화</h3>
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400">데이터 소스: 안산시 인구현황</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="h-48">
                        <canvas id="demographicsChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Chart 2: Illegal Dumping volume of Ansan (2025) -->
                <div>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800" id="chart2Title">월별 쓰레기 무단투기 추이 (톤)</h3>
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400">데이터 소스: 안산 폐기물 수거정보</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="h-48">
                        <canvas id="dumpingChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- NAVIGATION TABS -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 border-b border-slate-200 pb-px mb-8">
            <button onclick="switchTab('camera-scanner')" id="tabBtn-camera-scanner" class="tab-btn px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold border-b-2 border-brand-500 text-brand-600 flex items-center gap-2 transition-all">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-camera"></i> <span id="tabCameraText">AI 스마트 카메라 진단</span>
            </button>
            <button onclick="switchTab('rules')" id="tabBtn-rules" class="tab-btn px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 hover:border-slate-300 flex items-center gap-2 transition-all">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot"></i> <span id="tab2Text">동네별 맞춤형 배출 규칙</span>
            </button>
            <button onclick="switchTab('mapSection')" id="tabBtn-mapSection" class="tab-btn px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 hover:border-slate-300 flex items-center gap-2 transition-all">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> <span id="tab3Text">스마트 배출 지도</span>
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- TAB CONTENT 1: AI CAMERA SCANNER -->
        <section id="tab-camera-scanner" class="tab-content block">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
                <!-- Camera / Capture Viewfinder (5 cols) -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-5 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2" id="camTitle">AI 분리배출 카메라 스캐너</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mb-4" id="camDesc">카메라로 쓰레기를 비추거나 직접 사진을 업로드해 보세요. 혹은 준비된 AI 테스트 샘플을 선택해 즉시 성능을 검증할 수 있습니다.</p>
                        
                        <!-- Camera Viewfinder (Simulated/Real) -->
                        <div class="relative bg-slate-900 rounded-xl overflow-hidden aspect-video md:aspect-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center border border-slate-800 shadow-inner">
                            <!-- Scanning line animation -->
                            <div id="scannerLine" class="absolute left-0 w-full h-1 bg-brand-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_#10b981] scan-line z-20 hidden"></div>
                            
                            <!-- Real video tag -->
                            <video id="webcam" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-10 hidden" autoplay playsinline></video>
                            
                            <!-- Static mockup content when camera is inactive -->
                            <div id="cameraMockup" class="text-center z-10 p-6">
                                <span class="text-5xl block animate-bounce">📸</span>
                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 mt-3 font-semibold" id="camStartBtnText">카메라 연결 대기 중...</p>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Image Preview Area -->
                            <img id="imagePreview" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-10 hidden" src="" alt="스캔 대상 이미지">

                            <!-- Corner overlays -->
                            <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-6 h-6 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-brand-500 z-20"></div>
                            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 w-6 h-6 border-t-4 border-r-4 border-brand-500 z-20"></div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 w-6 h-6 border-b-4 border-l-4 border-brand-500 z-20"></div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 w-6 h-6 border-b-4 border-r-4 border-brand-500 z-20"></div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Camera Control Buttons -->
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mt-4">
                            <button onclick="startWebcam()" class="py-2.5 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-all">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-video"></i> <span id="btnStartCam">카메라 켜기</span>
                            </button>
                            <button onclick="triggerCapture()" id="captureBtn" class="py-2.5 bg-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-600 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-all disabled:opacity-50" disabled>
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-dot"></i> <span id="btnTakePic">촬영 및 분석</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>

                        <div class="relative flex py-4 items-center">
                            <div class="flex-grow border-t border-slate-100"></div>
                            <span class="flex-shrink mx-4 text-slate-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider" id="orLabel">또는 파일 업로드</span>
                            <div class="flex-grow border-t border-slate-100"></div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Image upload form -->
                        <label class="w-full flex flex-col items-center px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 text-slate-500 rounded-xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-100 transition-all text-center">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-arrow-up text-lg text-brand-500 mb-1"></i>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold" id="uploadBtnText">디바이스에서 사진 올리기</span>
                            <input type="file" id="fileInput" accept="image/*" class="hidden" onchange="handleImageUpload(event)">
                        </label>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Sandbox Samples for easy testing -->
                    <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
                        <h4 class="text-xs font-black uppercase text-slate-400 tracking-wider mb-3" id="sampleTitle">AI 분석 테스트용 샘플 선택</h4>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                            <button onclick="testWithSample('ramen')" class="p-2.5 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-brand-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-brand-300 rounded-xl text-left transition-all">
                                <span class="text-lg block">🍜</span>
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold block text-slate-700" id="smRamen">오염된 라면 용기</span>
                                <span class="text-[9px] text-red-500 font-semibold" id="smRamenStat">오염도 높음 (85%)</span>
                            </button>
                            <button onclick="testWithSample('pet')" class="p-2.5 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-brand-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-brand-300 rounded-xl text-left transition-all">
                                <span class="text-lg block">🥤</span>
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold block text-slate-700" id="smPet">투명 생수 페트병</span>
                                <span class="text-[9px] text-emerald-500 font-semibold" id="smPetStat">깨끗함 (5%)</span>
                            </button>
                            <button onclick="testWithSample('box')" class="p-2.5 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-brand-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-brand-300 rounded-xl text-left transition-all">
                                <span class="text-lg block">📦</span>
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold block text-slate-700" id="smBox">송장 붙은 택배 상자</span>
                                <span class="text-[9px] text-amber-500 font-semibold" id="smBoxStat">보통 오염 (40%)</span>
                            </button>
                            <button onclick="testWithSample('delivery')" class="p-2.5 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-brand-50 border border-slate-100 hover:border-brand-300 rounded-xl text-left transition-all">
                                <span class="text-lg block">🥡</span>
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold block text-slate-700" id="smDeli">음식물 묻은 배달기</span>
                                <span class="text-[9px] text-red-500 font-semibold" id="smDeliStat">오염도 극심 (95%)</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- AI Analysis & Solution Card (7 cols) -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <!-- Standard Solution Content -->
                    <div id="analysisResultView">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                            <span class="bg-brand-500 text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm"><i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i></span>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800" id="aiResultTitle">AI 실시간 진단 결과 리포트</h3>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Real-time Loading Indicator -->
                        <div id="aiLoading" class="hidden py-12 text-center">
                            <div class="inline-block animate-spin rounded-full h-10 w-10 border-4 border-brand-500 border-t-transparent mb-4"></div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700" id="loadingMsg">스마트 인공지능이 재질 및 오염도를 정밀 연산 중입니다...</p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Actual Result Layout -->
                        <div id="aiSuccess" class="space-y-6">
                            <!-- Score dashboard -->
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 text-center">
                                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 block" id="lblDetMat">감지된 재질</span>
                                    <span id="resMaterial" class="text-lg font-black text-slate-800 block mt-1">플라스틱 (PET)</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
                                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 block" id="lblDetCont">오염도 측정 수치</span>
                                    <span id="resContPercent" class="text-2xl font-black text-emerald-500 block mt-1">5%</span>
                                    <div class="w-full bg-slate-200 h-1 absolute bottom-0 left-0">
                                        <div id="resContProgress" class="bg-emerald-500 h-1 transition-all duration-1000" style="width: 5%"></div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 text-center">
                                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 block" id="lblDetGrade">배출 가능 등급</span>
                                    <span id="resGrade" class="text-lg font-black text-emerald-600 block mt-1">즉시 배출 가능</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Illustrated Guide Card -->
                            <div class="bg-brand-50/40 p-6 rounded-xl border border-brand-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6">
                                <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm text-center w-full md:w-32 flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center">
                                    <span class="text-5xl" id="resIcon">🥤</span>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-bold mt-2 bg-brand-100 text-brand-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full" id="resSubname">투명 페트병</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex-grow">
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                                        <span class="text-xs font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-brand-500 text-white" id="resStatusBadge">분리배출 적합</span>
                                        <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-slate-800" id="resTitle">이대로 분리 배출하셔도 좋습니다.</h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs leading-relaxed" id="resDesc">
                                        이물질 오염이 없어 깨끗한 상태입니다. 투명 페트병은 깨끗이 비우고 라벨을 제거한 후 전용 수거함에 압착하여 배출해 주시기 바랍니다.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Dynamic Checklist based on AI Scan -->
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-black uppercase text-slate-400 tracking-wider mb-4" id="lblActionCheck">배출 전 필수 액션 가이드</h4>
                                <ul class="space-y-3" id="resChecklist">
                                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                        <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></span>
                                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-600">내용물을 완전히 비웠습니다.</span>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                        <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></span>
                                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-600">라벨 스티커를 안전하게 떼어냈습니다.</span>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Fine Warning under the scan result -->
                    <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl border border-amber-100 flex items-start gap-3">
                        <span class="text-amber-500 mt-0.5 text-lg"><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i></span>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-amber-900 block" id="warnCamTitle">주의 및 과태료 규정 (Fine Policy)</span>
                            <span class="text-[11px] text-amber-700 leading-relaxed" id="warnCamDesc">오염된 용기를 그냥 배출하거나 비닐 라벨을 분리하지 않을 시 안산시 조례에 따라 폐기물 무단투기로 간주되어 최대 100만 원 이하의 과태료가 발생할 수 있습니다.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- TAB CONTENT 2: LOCALIZED CUSTOM DISCHARGE RULES (ALL 25 DONGS) -->
        <section id="tab-rules" class="tab-content hidden">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Neighborhood Selector & Demographic Status -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-1 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4" id="selectDongTitle">동네를 선택해 주세요</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mb-4" id="selectDongDesc">실제 안산시 인구현황 데이터를 기반으로 각 동네별 거주 외국인 비율 및 맞춤 배출일 정보를 제공합니다.</p>
                        
                        <!-- All 25 Dongs classified by District -->
                        <div class="relative mb-6">
                            <select id="dongSelect" onchange="onDongChange(this.value)" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 text-slate-800 text-sm rounded-xl focus:ring-brand-500 focus:border-brand-500 p-3 font-semibold cursor-pointer">
                                <optgroup label="상록구 (Sangrok-gu)">
                                    <option value="il" selected>일동 (Il-dong)</option>
                                    <option value="i">이동 (I-dong)</option>
                                    <option value="sa">사동 (Sa-dong)</option>
                                    <option value="sai">사이동 (Sai-dong)</option>
                                    <option value="haeyang">해양동 (Haeyang-dong)</option>
